OL,3,CProtests held over proposed site of
OL,4,Cnew Frimley Park Hospital
OL,6,FPeople against the proposed location
OL,7,Fof a new hosptial in Frimley say they
OL,8,Fare concerned for local infrastructure
OL,9,Fand that the plans would destroy acres
OL,10,Fof precious woodland.
OL,12,FFrimley Health NHS Foundation Trust
OL,13,Fannounced that land occupied by Pine
OL,14,FRidge Golf Club and surrounding
OL,15,Fwoodland was the preferred location
OL,16,Ffor a new Frimley Park Hospital.
OL,18,FThe land is currently owned by the
OL,19,Fcharity Frimley Fuel Allotments, which
OL,20,Fhas agreed to a sale in principle -
OL,21,Fallowing further assessment work.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
