OL,3,CProtests held over proposed site of
OL,4,Cnew Frimley Park Hospital
OL,6,FHowever local residents and
OL,7,Fcampaigners gathered on Tuesday
OL,8,Fmorning against the announcement.
OL,10,FOne demonstrator said the proposals
OL,11,Fwere 'proposterous', arguing that
OL,12,Fthere isn't 'appropriate
OL,13,Finfrastructure' and that the building
OL,14,Fof the site would destroy precious
OL,15,Fwoodland.
OL,17,FAnother said: "There are six schools
OL,18,Fthat will be impinged by the route
OL,19,Fbetween here and where they want to
OL,20,Fput the new hospital. It is totally
OL,21,Fgridlocked there."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
