FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781687892
OL,3,CProtests held over proposed site of
OL,4,Cnew Frimley Park Hospital
OL,6,FThose out demonstrating say they are
OL,7,Fnot opposed to a new hospital - but
OL,8,Fthat they believe it would be in the
OL,9,Fwrong location.
OL,11,FOne man said: "It is madness when
OL,12,Fthere is ample opportunity to build on
OL,13,Fcurrent sites that already have
OL,14,Finfrastructure."
OL,16,FA petition calling for Frimley Fuel
OL,17,FAllotments to reject any sale for
OL,18,Fdevelopment has obtained more than
OL,19,F11,600 signatures.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
